data.description: *Back on the market due to Buyer's financing being turned down*  Must see this French Provincial-style home on lush 6.3 acres in a quiet beautiful estate lot, small neighborhood. Walk into foyer, beautiful chandelier, high ceilings and tall doors, over sized master and bath. Upstairs off large kitchen with eat in area for large table, 2 more large bedrooms, loft area and full jack and Jill bath. Full finished basement complete in 2021 with full kitchen, flex area for living room or game room, 2 bedrooms, full bath, and large unfinished area. Home has solar panels that were installed in 2022 and large deck and private backyard. Home is 7-10 minutes from 85 *Please click on 3D Home tour in listing*    **Seller has an assumable VA loan.  This could mean huge savings for a buyer!
